 USB path: /sys/class/udc/38100000.usb 
 SoC temp: /sys/class/thermal/thermal_zone0/temp
 Bat. Current: /sys/class/power_supply/max777x9_battery/current_now

Power: 116 (KEY_POWER)
Volume Up: 115 (KEY_VOLUMEUP)
Volume Down: 114 (KEY_VOLUMEDOWN)
Expected Path: /dev/input/event0 or event1.
Uses the [gpio-keys] driver

What to know: You must find the string in /sys/class/udc/. For this chipset, it is almost certainly 38100000.usb.
Why it matters: Your configfs script will fail to "activate" the terminal or the data pipe unless you echo that exact string into the UDC file.